biography.text:
Grammy Award-nominated and Global chart topping Artist/Writer/Producer duo Goodboys are a rare talent. Their infectious hooks and melodies drive their music straight to the memory of anyone fortunate enough to hear them and has taken them to multi-platinum success all around the world.
 
From meeting each other in 2014, best mates Josh Grimmett and Ethan Shore shared a passion for electronic and pop music and now bring their unique style to the global stage. Their sound blends the dark energy of dance music, with the poppier, melodic, user-friendly euphoria more commonly heard on the radio, happily striking a perfect balance between the two. 

Their debut release, ‘Piece Of Your Heart’ with Meduza, has now seen over a billion streams globally, reaching double platinum (1.2m units) in the UK alone and peaking at #2 on the Official UK Charts. This trend has followed globally, with multi Diamond, Platinum and Gold certifications around the world and a GRAMMY nomination.

The follow up, ‘Lose Control’ with Becky Hill, has made an unprecedented impact, reaching the UK Top40 in its first week, now notching upward of 450 million cumulative streams, reaching platinum sales in the UK.
